  <scopecontent id="aspace_c837caa6cb132cc55af70999869fba3f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes a draft and revision of George Downs Wheeler's autobiography; herd records kept by Charles A. Wheeler; legal documents; family Bible records; genealogy; letters; financial records; and other family papers. Other names in the collection include W. (Mollie) Wheeler; W. A. Gregory; Charles P. Knapp; Henry M. Gregory; William Oringron; Silas Crandall; Thaddeus Mather; William Hawley; William Wheeler; Royal Wheeler; Robert Turner; James Turner; Mrs. George Hewitt; John Peters; Rachel Crandall; Addison J. Wheeler; Asa Babcock; and John Dickinson.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_b0d74940ef5507168cf30f94c33ed037">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Wheeler family papers, #3878. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
